               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>An incomplete copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Orucoṟpalaporuṭpeyartokuti</title> (chapter 11) of the <title xml:lang="ta">Cūṭāmaṇi Nikaṇṭu</title>, text with a commentary. Up to <title xml:lang="ta">Vakara Etukai</title>.</p>
<p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Orucoṟpalaporuṭpeyartokuti</title>, "section [on] the nouns [with] many meanings [for] a single word", deals with polysemic words.</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (**** 2023).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>     </summary>
                  
